{"tid":1469453,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[撐手足] 咩叫核彈都唔割? 記住狗都有豬隊友","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:15:04.000Z","uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb0110425bc092ff12ad3a7dde62ed898a97a04","tid":1469453,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:54:13.000Z","msg":"唔好見P牌屌左先, 利申有夢遊, 噚晚有入雞場<br />\n<br />\n喂點解813咁多人屌我地阻到遊客就係錯? 812冇阻到遊客咩?<br />\n咁衰乜? 就係812多人到要行入雞場, 多人到塞死路面, 塞爆機鐵站, AA就鳩縮<br />\n813剩係阻人入閘, AA根本唔撚驚你, 結果全晚夜晚2300-0200因航<strong>所有</strong>長途機全部走晒<br />\n唔信去 <a href=\"http://www.hongkongairport.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0bZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=86a66040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hongkongairport.com</a> 慢慢睇<br />\n<br />\n咁點解812成功813失敗呀?<br />\n因為我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">三分鐘熱度, 唔撚夠人</span></span></strong><br />\n要光復香港, 要打長期戰, 搞得AA一日, 結果冇用<br />\n如果813大家又要行入雞場, 驚鳩咩! 唔出黎既你地點對得住冇左隻眼既FA手足呀!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">屌晒你地呀!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之但係, 不合作運動, 講到尾就係要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">增加正苦管治成本</span></strong><br />\n阻到遊客又點? 改機票成本咪等AA, 跪低左既兩間航空公司, 同埋保險公司搞囉!<br />\n喂我地塞紅隧當中有冇遊客?<br />\n喺尖咀狗屋喺正Park Lane門口當中有冇遊客?<br />\n記住, 支拿豬都係遊客黎!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">總之核爆都唔撚割</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁之後點做? 我唔係大台, 個人意見歡迎討論歡迎屌<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好嘥時間捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n有十萬隻鬼我地捉得幾多個? 同埋有鬼有乜問題?<br />\n記住<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬼都有豬隊友</span></span></strong><br />\n最成功嗰日係邊日? 71嘛! 上晒New York Times頭條<br />\n71下晝1330, 最多和理非諗住出黎行嗰時有鬼衝玻璃, 結果由200萬人跌到55萬出黎行<br />\n但我地咪<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將錯就錯</span></span></strong>爆入去立法會練字上頭條囉<br />\n<br />\n鬼豬隊友仲有721西鐵打大肚婆, 結果民意向我地, 例子多不勝數<br />\n記住, 鬼係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑社會 毅進仔</span></span></strong><br />\n黃藍最大分別係乜? 黃係學歷高年紀輕, 藍係相反<br />\n佢地除左係廢老外, <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲係低能架! 咁點會冇豬隊友</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2.勇武<br />\n各位勇武巴絲<br />\n點解唔去做老豆搵仔教我地做既嘢呀? <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">麻包袋</span></span></strong><br />\n有晒地址電話狗BB相, 你地唔驚喺鏡頭面前打狗, 唔敢做七警?<br />\n仲有英國巴絲, Six Degrees of Separation, 你唔係同我講你搭上搭唔識到淋奠兩個公子呀<br />\n有冇關心過佢地人生安全? 唔關心下, 點可以爭取<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">五大訴求</span></span></strong>?<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7929e061187d02c84fbaca1ceacac0eebf4edf47","tid":1469453,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa12423dfffedab2674f333d634d8612e52534f2","tid":1469453,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}